metadata.name: Shinobi Girl
metadata.description:
I wonder... if she is a real shinobi?...

Oh and those eyes, they must be able to glow at night, right?


---------
The collector will get the following files:

- An orginal GIF file in 1592*2200 pixel.

- 2 original PNG files (which are color and grayscale) in 2750*3800 pixel.
